description: This ice pop cart is putting a unique twist on the classic frozen treat you know and love!Handmade, wholesome, organic, and great, Gigi's Ice Lollies is showing your sweet tooth the amazing innovations available in the world of icy cold flavor today.Are you a spiced rhubarb & pomegranate person, or more of a strawberry basil? Maybe you're in the mood for Frozen hot chocolate. Whatever you crave, Gigi's is ready.Buckle in and get ready for some awesome new ways to keep cool on the go, with Gigi's Ice Lollies!
name: Gigi's Ice Lollies
